OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and settled, with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine for most. Some patchy cloud
OL,8,Fmay linger around the coast at times.
OL,9,FFeeling warm, but chillier on coasts.
